---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - AB Brothers Construction"
  description="Privacy Policy for AB Brothers Construction Inc. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-primary py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <h1 class="text-primary-foreground">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-primary-foreground/75 mt-2 text-sm">Last updated: 5/26/2025</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-8">

        <p>At AB Brothers Construction Inc., your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect the personal information you provide to us through our website, lead forms, and other interactions with our business.</p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We may collect the following types of personal information:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Phone number</li>
            <li>Address (if provided in form)</li>
            <li>Project interests or details (if submitted in a message or inquiry)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">This information is typically collected when you:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Submit a contact form or lead form on our website</li>
            <li>Call or email us directly</li>
            <li>Interact with one of our ads (e.g., Google Ads lead form extensions)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We use the information we collect to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Respond to your inquiries or service requests</li>
            <li>Schedule consultations or estimates</li>
            <li>Provide project-related updates or information</li>
            <li>Send occasional promotional or follow-up emails (you can opt out at any time)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not sell or share your information with third parties for their own marketing purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We may share your personal information with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Trusted service providers who help us operate our business (e.g., CRM platforms, email services)</li>
            <li>Legal authorities if required by law</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">5. Your Choices</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">You may contact us at any time to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
            <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your information</li>
            <li>Opt out of any future communications</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">6. Google Advertising Disclosure</h2>
          <p>We may use Google Ads and other digital advertising services to promote our business. These services may collect information about your interaction with our ads. For more information on how Google uses data, visit: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">Google's advertising policies</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-foreground mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please feel free to contact us:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 text-foreground">
            <p>AB Brothers Construction Inc.</p>
            <p>Mount Lebanon, PA</p>
            <p>Phone: <a href="tel:4123788115" class="text-accent hover:underline">(412) 378-8115</a></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:abbrotherspgh@gmail.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">abbrotherspgh@gmail.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
